summary: I have a confession to make. I think Captain Marvel was just OK. It didn’t pump me up like other Marvel movies.  The battles...
body:
I have a confession to make. I think Captain Marvel was just OK.

It didn’t pump me up like other Marvel movies. 

The battles were exciting, Brie Larson was pretty good as Captain Marvel and Samuel Jackson was great as always. 

But…what’s up with the plot? It was pretty weak. I feel like we needed to know more about who Carrol was at that time and the conflict she was involved in before we could care about her past and relationships.

I feel they could’ve done more.
